OL,4,G2230FTrauma Room One
OL,5,     GAndrew, 63, faces urgent brain
OL,6,     Gsurgery to remove a tumour.
OL,7,     GSarah, 52, undergoes a brain
OL,8,     Gimplant procedure in the hope of
OL,9,     Gending decades of excruciating
OL,10,     Gcluster headaches.
OL,11,G2330FA&E After Dark
OL,12,     GIn Rotherham's A&E a patient with
OL,13,     Ga suspected head injury is under
OL,14,     Garrest in the car park. In
OL,15,     GLondon, an eye injury from mixing
OL,16,     Gconcrete requires action to
OL,17,     Gprevent permanent damage.
